    "由“反馈助理”收集的诊断数据可能包含个人信息。你可以在提交前轻点查看附加数据，或向左轻扫删除。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The diagnose datas collected by Feedback Assistant may contains personal informations. You can tap to check attached datas before submitting, or swipe left to delete."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "由“反馈助理”收集的诊断数据可能包含个人信息。你可以在提交前轻点查看附加数据，或向左轻扫删除。"
